data.title: Homepage
data.meta_description: Eliassen Group provides strategic consulting solutions for clients, driving results across diverse industries, markets and technologies of the future.
data.text:
Your Partner for Human-Powered Solutions

Eliassen is the go-to partner for human-powered solutions and world-class expertise attuned to your unique needs and business goals.

End-to-End Services to Support You Every Step of the Way

Eliassen Group is here to help you succeed throughout every phase of your business journey with our comprehensive portfolio of services and capabilities.

Decades of Proven Success

For over 30 years, we’ve provided the human power for technology, business, and clinical initiatives on behalf of thousands of companies. As your trusted partner, we can do the same for you.

Empowering Transformation for People and Organizations Looking to Reach Further

By providing the highest-quality services, industry-leading technologies, top-notch expertise and talent, and proven best practices, we’ll help you achieve your goals faster.

Eliassen Group

Eliassen is a leading strategic consulting company that provides business, clinical, and IT services for our clients as they seek to transform and execute strategies that will drive exceptional outcomes.

Extensive Teams, Talent, and Resources Customized for your Needs

Eliassen goes beyond solving short-term business and technology needs. Instead, we develop holistic solutions and sound business strategies based on what’s important to you.
